American actress, Busy Philipps, celebrated her 40th birthday in a grand style by hosting a lavish Mexican destination wedding in marrying herself. Philipps took to her Instagram handle @busyphilipps to share the concept behind the bash, where she posted a photo of herself in the stunning dress. “So I was thinking about turning 40. And it is weird because my perpetual age is 19. Sometimes 27 depending but now I’m 40 (my birthday is the 25th actually) HOW AM I 40 YEARS OLD? “Anyway, I decided I wanted to throw myself a destination wedding (to myself) for my 40th at one of my favorite places in the world @florafarms in Cabo.